{"tid":1263044,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"今朝幫老母登記咗做選民","createTime":"2019-06-28T03:38:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-28T04:11:50.000Z","uid":131731,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4dfb996ee0e0f4c7ccb423c17403487fb627d60d","tid":1263044,"uid":131731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T03:38:24.000Z","msg":"平時佢都只係想平平無奇安安份份噉過日子, 好多野都唔會點過問<br />\n但呢個月發生啲野, 再加上我不停數臭港共政權, 班仆街點賣港, 幾咁冷血 etc, 佢都選擇咗要企出黎投票踢走班仆街保皇黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位年青人, 當連啲老一輩都識盡公民責任做選民投票嘅時候, 你地唔係諗住嫌麻煩就由佢啊?<br />\n填份form係2分鐘都唔使, 我呼籲大家未登記嘅就快啲登記, 順手幫埋屋企人/叫埋身邊啲朋友仔登記!<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-1%28C&d=UUYXYMm1a91OOf%2FewiyebQKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=08c0df52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C</a>).pdf<br />\n每一票都好重要! 香港人要企出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3db793437e00e9422e52cbcc3661bd0cb8234125","tid":1263044,"uid":258192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T03:41:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5c85da18bc634e86f484434dbe9dd282b9737705","tid":1263044,"uid":131731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T03:42:56.000Z","msg":"求下大家快啲登記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就黎dead喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40ff663384e35c7cdf3b2fee08a05c1a24d43a34","tid":1263044,"uid":209225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3db793437e00e9422e52cbcc3661bd0cb8234125","tid":1263044,"uid":258192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T03:41:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T03:43:57.000Z","msg":"今晚七點立會煲底集會呀！熱門連一個post都無提呢單！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1262862\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.k